  "description": "Blend sits at 0.4 — leaning into memory, each note a reconstruction of dissolving grain traces. Mod wheel (CC#1) opens the shutter toward full perception: at full throw, the blend pushes to 0.4 + offset toward present-tense Opsis. The past recedes in real time as your hand rises. A gesture that decides how much you remember.",
